    When I execute the findChildNodes query for parent node aggregate id "a2a" and filter '{"ordering": [{"type": "propertyName", "field": "text", "direction": "ASCENDING"}]}' I expect the nodes "a2a1,a2a2,a2a4,a2a5" to be returned
